title: The Satanic Plot to Reduce Earth's Population
cleaned_text: What’s the common thread between man-made viruses, late-term abortions, damaging vaccinations, climate change indoctrination, legalization of drugs, and the promotion of a multi-gender society? A very dark plot that isn’t hidden anymore! Join Amir as he uses the word of God to unveil the satanic plot to reduce the earth’s population.
